<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <!-- 高潮分裂 -->
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.label>高潮不稳定</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.label>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.description>携带此基因的小人在高潮时会变得更加不稳定——一旦达到临界水平，他们将启动分裂过程。</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.description>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.0.label>稳定</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.0.label>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.1.label>烦躁</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.1.label>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.2.label>不稳定</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.2.label>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.3.label>危急</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.3.label>

  <rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.label>分裂震荡</rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.label>
  <rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.description>最近经历了（成功的）分裂。由于这一过程极为耗费体力，需要一定时间来恢复。在恢复期间，不能再开始新的分裂。</rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.description>
  <rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.stages.0.label>渐退</rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.stages.0.label>
  <rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.stages.1.label>新鲜</rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.stages.1.label>

</LanguageData>